description: Welcome to the 765 Condominiums located in the bustling east side of September - already 75% reserved! 765 East Third Street will include a collection of 25 residences with high end finishes, ample parking and a luxurious lobby with several seating areas and a fireplace.  Each residence includes 1 parking space with the option to purchase an additional parking space.  Interior kitchen finishes include Fisher & Paykel appliances, Calacatta Venetian Bronze countertops, Metropolitan cabinetry and a Porcelanosa backsplash.  Additional finishes include Porcelanosa tiled bathrooms, thermostatic shower control system and Toto dual flush elongated toilets. Several residences have expansive balconies with gas-lines. The 765 Condominiums are nearby to several of Boston's best beaches, including M Street Beach and Castle Island. Additional neighborhood amenities include the Curley Center, M Street Park, dozens of restaurants and bars and the nearby Seaport District.
